data.description: Surround yourself in Mother Nature’s Wonderland on 5 acres of rural landscape in the Melon Valley, Buhl, Idaho.  This single-story home has been completely remodeled with 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. New HVAC, LVP flooring, carpet and lighting.  Enjoy the new, open concept, kitchen, dining room and spacious living room.  Tidy up, in two brand new bathrooms.  This lovely home is freshly painted inside and out.  Solar panels are included to keep your electric expenses extra low.  The property also includes 5 water shares.  Enjoy incredible views from the picture windows.
